{"tid":1493081,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【被代表】政府對話平台成員星期六進行首次會面","createTime":"2019-08-21T05:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T06:24:55.000Z","uid":53003,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"4ada95b99f5ec43f8e49e9d7a2dab46537d8d7ae","tid":1493081,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:59:08.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥昨日提出邀請各界人士組成對話平台。據了解，獲邀的人士會來自政界、宗教界及教育界等不同界別，星期六會進行首次會面，人數約二十至三十人，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">包括前政務司司長唐英年、前運房局局長張炳良、天主教香港教區宗座署理湯漢、教大校長張仁良同浸大校長錢大康等。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唐英年早前指如果特首需要他提供意見，非常樂意提供協助。錢大康亦歡迎成立對話平台的建議，形容是「千里之行，始於足下」，可以讓社會各界有機會展開持續對話，加深彼此之間的了解，並促成社會和解。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1155548&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1155548%26csid%3D261_341&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9og8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=e52bc9e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1155548&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"bd91f4a6098ad7492596d502f67d134465a1007c","tid":1493081,"uid":183758,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:59:53.000Z","msg":"你見過啲人冇用㗎喎"},{"pid":"c75aa3d79aca00535632ed6a2423378611eea805","tid":1493081,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd91f4a6098ad7492596d502f67d134465a1007c","tid":1493081,"uid":183758,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:59:53.000Z","msg":"你見過啲人冇用㗎喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:00:10.000Z","msg":"嗰"},{"pid":"20662bfc098736f5b2f2d1baa67c86172ef2a5c2","tid":1493081,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:01:11.000Z","msg":"無人會聽佢地枝笛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24b3dc7045adcd2a7b62fcaf9d5fc610373ff41","tid":1493081,"uid":22677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime